<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Hollywood couple Judd Apatow and Leslie Mann were spotted enjoying a stroll in Los Angeles this Saturday.</p>

<p>The 48-year-old cut a summery figure in a pink floral skirt with some lace fringe around its hemline.</p>

<p>Meanwhile her 52-year-old director husband wore a brownish grey polo shirt with casual black shorts and white sneakers.</p>

<p>Time together: Hollywood couple Judd Apatow and Leslie Mann were spotted enjoying a stroll in Los Angeles this Saturday</p>

<p>In one heartwarming moment the duo could be seen apparently skipping while arm in arm in a parking lot. </p>

<p>Both of them made sure to wear masks before heading out on their walk in keeping with coronavirus safety protocols.</p>

<p>Leslie showed off her still amazingly trim figure in a skintight white tank top and wore her blonde hair down.</p>

<p>Having fun: In one heartwarming moment the duo could be seen apparently skipping while arm in arm in a parking lot</p>

<p>Both of them brought sunglasses with them though Judd hung them from his neckline while Leslie kept hers on her face.</p>

<p>She complemented her ensemble with a pair of pink Gucci slippers that featured the brand's logo in silver on the straps.</p>

<p>The pair have been married since 1997 and share daughters Maude, 22, and Iris, 17, who have both become actresses like their mother.</p>

<p>Stylish: The 48-year-old cut a summery figure in a pink floral skirt with some lace fringe around its hemline</p>

<p>Along with being his wife Leslie has also acted in multiple of Judd's projects including movies like The 40-Year-Old Virgin, Knocked Up and This Is 40.</p>

<p>Leslie was not featured in Judd's latest film The King Of Staten Island starring Pete Davidson - however Maude did have a role in the movie.</p>

<p>Next year Leslie will be seen as leading lady Elvira in a film adaptation of Noel Coward's beloved darkly comic play Blithe Spirit.</p>
